  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Gazrot Goresnappa is dead beneath the head of his own Gargant, and every boss big enough to smell opportunity wants the title of Warboss. A prophecy points to a mysterious gate under the human city below, promising that whoever finds it first can turn the galaxy green. Da Genrul of the Blood Axes trusts discipline and plans; Zagnob Thundaskuzz of the Evil Sunz trusts speed; Mag Dedfist of the Goffs trusts fists; Snaggi Littletoof trusts that even a grot uprising can have its day. An Ork succession comedy with real teeth, where greenskin politics are absurd, violent, and entirely functional.",
